{
  "stem": "293.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have offer from every high school in Poland, but I stay first in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I will tell you right now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1938, I got a wonderful job in the brand new Jewish high school in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Magnificent school, with the best teachers what the money can buy, what they selected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they can only lure them there to the little town from city of Cracow or Warsaw, or or [NON-ENGLISH] or [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wilno ?] by giving a almost double salary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- [LAUGHS] you must understand, I mean, this time I was 24-- no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In this time, I was 26 years old, and I was getting close to 300 American US dollar a month.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't think so anybody in America in 1937 or '38 got so much money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took the job, and over there, till the 1939, I was-- the last two year, '38, '39, I was teaching there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was beautiful two years for me as a young man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I came back to Cracow when the war started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was teaching in city of Krakow in the Hebrew gymnasium, one the best and most prominent high school in Poland, Jewish high school in Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war coming, I was-- I was-- mobilization came to me with a secret telephone call because I was train as a company commander.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the same day, in 19-- and I was 1930, I got the order to go immediately to my unit, what was in [NON-ENGLISH], was 100, 200 kilometers away from Cracow, in east, toward east.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I arrive there Friday morning, at about 4 o'clock in the morning. 6 o'clock, the war started, and the first planes was bombing-- bombing all the barracks and the-- the the regiment.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
